title: Mythology - Native American Indian Myths (pdf) EarthBow
description:
EarthBow - Native American Indian Myths, 2005, 728 pages

Containing more than 300 myths, legends, and tales from dozens of tribes, this book is perhaps the most extensive collection of Native American folklore ever published.
